{"tid":1524804,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"手足請停止一切割席及分化行為","createTime":"2019-08-31T18:16:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T18:19:34.000Z","uid":309617,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ac97dbc894cd325d37c38ee09f3ee9e110343386","tid":1524804,"uid":309617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:16:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">黎明前嘅黑暗，係至撚黑暗！</span></span><br />\n831我相信係由6.9後香港最撚黑暗嘅一日。<br />\n謹記手足們，我哋仲有大把路未行完，犬群做埋啲戇鳩行為嘅時候，都冇選擇割席分化。<br />\n身為<span style=\"color: gold;\">正義之師</span>嘅我哋，仲憑咩理由去分化呀屌。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成日話設死線升級設死線升級，人哋犬群冇撚設過死線都升到咁高級，我哋唔係仲要忍呀嘛。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">支共，港腐，犬群，黑社會，黨鐵。</span>我哋依家有五大主要敵人，香港人咁可愛咁聰明，一定諗到辦法點樣去抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先我哋聽日9.1機場要走定留，唔該要攞咗個共識先，要齊上齊落。 政腐一日唔回應我哋嘅訴求，我哋一日都仲可以玩蛋，打出香港人嘅經濟牌。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後相信大家對跳高運動都有所興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，歡迎香港人套用落生活之中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，唔鍾意做運動嘅，又可以研究下出入閘機內部運作，唔使再話冇資料喺手頭上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於我經常認為香港作為一個轉口港，唔輸出番啲嘢，真係對唔住我哋香港核心價值。中國內地咁大個市場，唔係放棄佢吓話。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有4000蚊啲個人資料表格好鍾意放落麻包袋度，我哋香港人咁尊敬香港警察，等佢地收工唔係唔禮貌地報答下佢哋。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最重要唔好唔記得，禍...你老母呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，梗係多啲關懷下警察兒女，報答下佢哋父母親。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最尾江湖中人最重要就係講義氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，同佢哋講錢冇用㗎。知道啲白底商戶仲同佢哋講錢？係香港人嘅梗係成班人講義氣，拍下心口拍下玻璃，支持下佢哋啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要推倒希特拉，首先要搞掂佢嘅軍隊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命！</span></span><br />\n<br />\nStand with Hong Kong<br />\nFight for Freedom!"},{"pid":"041370ef85f4c74fe496d5c1b574823a012fe57a","tid":1524804,"uid":309617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:17:41.000Z","msg":"p牌自推十連<br />\n1"},{"pid":"67966ab67a89060ea37b4074c6bf58483011192c","tid":1524804,"uid":309617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:17:53.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"3edfefaab895c9ecf7161863456004c81b157a29","tid":1524804,"uid":309617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:18:03.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"359a4ab28cbe9c21554c0616e8809465243128c3","tid":1524804,"uid":309617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:18:17.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"6b7fadcd16767d73270b86740040e6b2f515ee76","tid":1524804,"uid":309617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:18:27.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"18d8341e78d8c0ff7112036040579499773340ac","tid":1524804,"uid":309617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:18:37.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"e6003a89bd19e8446563e71a86a0ae248131d2f2","tid":1524804,"uid":309617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:18:47.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"a042d50e792617a098c4959931db8d693c505fa6","tid":1524804,"uid":309617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:18:57.000Z","msg":"8/10"},{"pid":"ec5e0a6d4d601c2c4901c412878be80875d0f21e","tid":1524804,"uid":309617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:19:08.000Z","msg":"9/10"},{"pid":"3314842054fa45f8d4cba081560317942352d549","tid":1524804,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:19:12.000Z","msg":"我知大家好撚嬲, 因為我地冇清算黨鐵先搞到今日咁, 但係要記得今日要去春袋報仇, 黨鐵黎緊一齊再清算！香港人加油 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lz7uo3t.jpg\" data-thumbna